<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en"><head><meta charSet="utf-8"/><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width"/><link rel="icon" href=""/><title>Mighty Oaks International Nursery &amp; Kindergarten | At Mighty Oaks, we are an international nursery and kindergarten that nurtures young minds through a trilingual education (English, Putonghua, and Cantonese) designed for children aged 8 months to 6 years. Our programs include playgroup, nursery, kindergarten, and exciting seasonal camps, all centered on a play-based curriculum and character-building activities. With an award winning campus in Kennedy Town, we provide a safe, stimulating, and inclusive environment where every child thrives emotionally, socially, and intellectually. Join us to empower your child on their journey from little acorns to mighty oaks!</title><meta http-equiv="Content-Language" content="en"/><meta name="keywords" content=""/><meta name="title" property="og:title" content="Mighty Oaks International Nursery &amp; Kindergarten | At Mighty Oaks, we are an international nursery and kindergarten that nurtures young minds through a trilingual education (English, Putonghua, and Cantonese) designed for children aged 8 months to 6 years. Our programs include playgroup, nursery, kindergarten, and exciting seasonal camps, all centered on a play-based curriculum and character-building activities. With an award winning campus in Kennedy Town, we provide a safe, stimulating, and inclusive environment where every child thrives emotionally, socially, and intellectually. Join us to empower your child on their journey from little acorns to mighty oaks!"/><meta name="twitter:title" content="Mighty Oaks International Nursery &amp; Kindergarten | At Mighty Oaks, we are an international nursery and kindergarten that nurtures young minds through a trilingual education (English, Putonghua, and Cantonese) designed for children aged 8 months to 6 years. Our programs include playgroup, nursery, kindergarten, and exciting seasonal camps, all centered on a play-based curriculum and character-building activities. With an award winning campus in Kennedy Town, we provide a safe, stimulating, and inclusive environment where every child thrives emotionally, socially, and intellectually. Join us to empower your child on their journey from little acorns to mighty oaks!"/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary"/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.mightyoaks.edu.hk/favicon.ico"/><meta name="description" property="og:description" content=""/><meta name="twitter:description" content=""/><meta name="google-site-verification" content="idq2MgDU66QZ4rjWsnvSlgZdrbOk6I3iI9uXzpDRGhs"/><meta name="google-site-verification" content="jSjJx0dbYxTXOJDe_RajuPL5bgL017LtBBvJlAq_ZkU"/><script>
